00:19:14,667 --> 00:19:17,125
<i>Estaremos bien aquí</i>

246
00:19:46,875 --> 00:19:48,875
Hey.

247
00:19:48,875 --> 00:19:51,458
¡Oh!

248
00:19:51,458 --> 00:19:53,500
Me alegro de verte.
